  <h2 class="sec-title" id="weatherTitle">When to Visit <em>Uttar Pradesh</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">UP has three seasons: blazing summer (April–June), monsoon (July–September) and a glorious cool winter (October–March). October to March is the golden window — the Taj Mahal glows in winter mist, Varanasi's ghats are at their most atmospheric and the entire pilgrim circuit is perfectly accessible.</p>
